# The Kitty runs fully out of the box with ZERO env vars (dry-run mode).
# These are only needed for --real Solana devnet settlement.

# ── Solana devnet RPC ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: https://api.devnet.solana.com (public). Any devnet RPC works.
# Get a dedicated one from: https://www.helius.dev or https://quicknode.com
#KITTY_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com

# ── Demo USD₮ mint (SPL) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Devnet has no canonical USD₮, so the demo uses a devnet SPL mint standing
# in for USD₮ (6 decimals — same as real USD₮). Create yours with:
#   spl-token create-token --decimals 6   (https://spl.solana.com/token)
# then fund each member: spl-token mint <MINT> 1000 <MEMBER_ATA>
#KITTY_TOKEN_MINT=YourDevnetMintAddressHere

# ── Responsible-play cap (USD₮ base units, 6 decimals) ───────────────
# The WDK Transaction Policy DENYs any transfer above this. 100 USD₮ default.
#KITTY_MAX_BUY_IN=100000000
